{"tid":1604984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線作戰指南","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:54:49.000Z","uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d484497b38386e2fdc132e2e83a234adef821fcd","tid":1604984,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"今次講兩樣野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 火魔法</span></span><br />\n唔中唔緊要<br />\n但係求下你地<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再燒到手足</span><br />\nAim 人 / 地下   就自己決定<br />\n講過核爆都唔割 更何況<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗已經殺左咁多手足</span><br />\n唔夠膽整嘅  就帶樽 麵粉 洗潔精 糖 屋企一定有啦<br />\n出到去搵手足整 <span style=\"color: red;\">一個人唔夠料 一班人總會夠</span><br />\n麻煩全部<span style=\"color: red;\">自己學下點整</span> 你唔整唔緊要 你見人做錯 提下佢都好<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.心態</span></span><br />\n如果到而家都仲係見到狗就驚嘅<br />\n請你行返後 唔好阻住<br />\n前線唔係見有事就跑 見到速龍就跑 見到防暴推緊又跑<br />\n咁你企咁前做乜<br />\n有一班手足遺書都寫埋 你好唔好意思同人地企埋一齊呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗拎長盾 根本唔會推得快</span> 又驚<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">速龍</span> 講左過百次 <span style=\"color: red;\">唔高防 人多一定夠打</span> 又驚<br />\n好心無咁嘅心理準備就唔好阻住啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Full gear 但係有咩事都淨係識跑 你羞唔羞恥?<br />\n新血唔係問題 但係連基本都做唔好 只會累死班手足</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"033b4e808b38fe0c121b2cf1a6adaad17cacaad7","tid":1604984,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"根本冇殺人 <br />\n唔好再吹水"},{"pid":"ae2235d3a3d145ac73df828eceea926231db447e","tid":1604984,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"push行動post"},{"pid":"9e08f9b019dfd1cc7dd68153b7250d07a8d221b8","tid":1604984,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"今晚需要一個集氣大會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604777</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f20406636b959c58b975893c29b91364a9302d8a","tid":1604984,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"push行動post<br />\n聽日就作戰la<br />\n有乜事有乜新聞遲一日就推"},{"pid":"22c33baa277ca4498fc23768497dd90b552723ef","tid":1604984,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"再唔檢查就輸得好慘"},{"pid":"92ce60fbb0e741ed854da600058b964573ba819e","tid":1604984,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"push"}]}